snippet.title: LIMINAL PHASE Gameplay Trailer - HD
snippet.description:
#vrgaming  #vrhorror #indiegame 
Gameplay trailer for our VR action horror game LIMINAL PHASE.
Wishlist on Steam 👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1999630/LIMINAL_PHASE/

About the game
LIMINAL PHASE is a VR action horror game set in a parallel ‘90s. Fight malevolent monsters, solve peculiar puzzles, and explore the dark corners of a fractured mind consumed by video games.

This trailer shows the standalone version. LIMINAL PHASE was featured in the Upload VR Showcase Summer 2022 and 2023.

By AlcA Studio: https://alcastudio.com/welcome
